**Location:** `/Users/jdsingh/Projects/AI/forge/src/factory/sandbox.rs`, lines 105-115

**Severity:** MEDIUM

**Code:**
```rust
pub async fn new(default_image: String) -> Option<Self> {
    let docker = Docker::connect_with_socket_defaults().ok()?;
